We designed a hypergeometric-based measurement (hygeSSI) to estimate the interactions between two binary-coded SNPs (dominant or recessive). The hypergeometric p-value for a pair of binary-coded SNPs with respect to a case–control cohort is calculated as follows:\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
